    "In the latter BOX 4.",
    "Analog (mixed signal) chips.",
    "BrainScales2 is a mixed-signal wafer-scale system that runs in 1000×-10,000× accelerated time and implements physical models of neurons and synapses 211.",
    "It comprises 512 neurons and 112k synapses per core with online spike-driven synaptic plasticity (SDSP).",
    "Recent benchmarking of this chip has shown that learning corrects for the mismatch (non-homogeneity of devices) present in the analog hardware 212."
